Recording Method:
IRI (minted Nomen) with Nomen properties
- has nomen string https://www.rdaregistry.info/Elements/n/#P80068  
- has scheme of nomen (from $2) https://www.rdaregistry.info/Elements/n/#P80069 
- has note on nomen (if $q) is present and follows $z in sequence)  https://www.rdaregistry.info/Elements/n/#P80071
- has status of nomen  http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/n/#P80168

LA 12/30/2024
Justification for Mapping: Mapped to current Manifestation, but with status of nomen cancelled/invalid
Transformation Notes:
Manifestation]-->rdamo:P30004-->[Nomen]-->rdan:P80068-->($z) .  [Nomen]--rdan:P80069-->($2) . 

[Nomen]-->rdan:P80071-->($q).
NOTE:  both $a and $z may appear in same tag.  If this is the case, only map a $q to the canceled/invalid/ nomen if it follows $z in sequence.  

[Nomen]--rdan:P80168--><http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/mstatus/cancinv> 
LA 10/11/2024

Justification for Mapping: Appliy to minted nomen from $a or $z using data from LC Source Codes table
Transformation Notes:
Lookup code in LC table https://www.loc.gov/standards/sourcelist/national-bibliography.html; and create two properties, one with the code and one with the citation.
[Nomen]--rdan:P80069-->($2)
[Nomen]--rdan:p80069-->"[textual citation of bibliography]"
